snippet.textDisplay: After all these years following Noorie, Strings and Coke Studio, the comparison between Kami Paul and Aahad Nayani has dwindled away more and more, except for one thing- Kami Bhai produces better rock beats and Aahad Bhai makes the best Hindostani Beats.
